{"tid":107354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚垃圾車贏到阿仙奴 我直播比狗屌","createTime":"2017-02-04T12:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T09:13:54.000Z","uid":2169,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4dadac678d9e3f7decf5331aab16f6049b30ff1","tid":107354,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"今場睇牌面阿仙奴真係䇔硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢今場11個有10個都係炒車3:0果班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有後備殺手黑b同銀河唯一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然無左沙加同藍斯 但一個幫對手博12m 一個成日派膠 真係無左仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反觀垃圾車都係勝十一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雷斯夏神有傷在身 表現實失準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沙皮上場射失12m 信心實大趺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n此消彼長下真係睇唔出垃圾車勝出既可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今場應該0:2<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：和同客都有3點幾倍<br />\n要上樓就快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c327c83e32d680d7ec5bbf2084a8894608cae86","tid":107354,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"等睇樓主又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daba46e4157661b75c05cda9efdb3e4f401bab75","tid":107354,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"穩了"},{"pid":"2c97517efa10e103e83f272d7c3c00ff97e3109b","tid":107354,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"阿狗有個臥底典贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5582305